{"tid":1615543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方曾多次被拍到疑似插贓嫁禍  口供及證據可信成疑","createTime":"2019-10-03T06:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T10:38:47.000Z","uid":15696,"like":409,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"bd730760e36037557705787e58eb9fec8d5a0453","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:33:11.000Z","msg":"【槍轟學生】警涉插贓嫁禍中槍男生畫面曝光！ 搜證警換4呎長削尖鐵枝作「武器」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HhcyKrM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHhcyKrM.jpg&h=a39a469a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10.1當日多區發生警民衝突，一名中五生曾志健於荃灣遭防暴警近距離向胸口開槍，現時仍然留院，警方今日即以參與暴動及襲警等罪控告他及另外6名涉案男子，案件下午在沙田裁判法院提堂。不過有傳媒拍到當日片段，清楚見到「健仔」被捕後倒地，原本其手持的白色枝桿於其身旁，但未有被警員取走，取而代之就是從遠處拿來一枝4呎長被削尖的鐵枝，連同「健仔」手持的浮板盾取走，疑為作為證物。<br />\n<br />\n香港警隊濫權濫捕，除混入示威人群中，更曾疑插贓嫁禍！now新聞台及香港大學學生會學苑即時新聞，分別拍攝到有警員在8月11日銅鑼灣清場中，疑插贓嫁禍示威者。其中在now新聞台的直播片段可見，一名身穿白衣的男士已被警員制服，當他背對一批警員時，有一名警員突然將一支竹枝放入該名男子的黑色背囊中。<br />\n而港大學生會學苑即時新聞也報道，有市民向在場記者表示，自己在被捕期間被警察毆打，而被捕後更有警員將一支竹放入自己背囊，示威者哭訴：「個警察放支竹落我背囊啊！」而學苑記者在現場拍攝的照片中所見，被捕的白衣市民背囊敞開，而旁邊的警察手扶竹枝，竹枝則放在背囊內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逆權運動】人人是記者 徵集網民好Q 質問克警高層"},{"pid":"a8989030fe01a8a36caebc62a2c390dd98d1d4ad","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/402334050471694/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F402334050471694%2F&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=b1bb168c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/402334050471694/</a>"},{"pid":"a6e24772dc7fdf3f767d72fc6a150750ba5507ed","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:36:47.000Z","msg":"香港01 全部當冇事發生<br />\n香港警察做咩都唔洗上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fab7d0815eec0e7b802ff472c083cbbe149ea47","tid":1615543,"uid":118652,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:37:42.000Z","msg":"告暴動都可以打甩<br />\n因為黑驚做扮演示威做出激烈行為"},{"pid":"56ae0d86a16220598d325b164323f825679474c1","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:39:15.000Z","msg":"枝白色嘢到最後當垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本一直都有插贓嫁禍"},{"pid":"a95dd993f0f9e168c59755872f5ad07bad770579","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:40:43.000Z","msg":"8月11日最尾結果點"},{"pid":"34049f8ecbeadc1e30b4e70e5f213272664f081f","tid":1615543,"uid":78470,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"琴晚黃大仙個阿伯拎刀斬人都當把刀係垃圾踢走啦<br />\n根本而家淨係砌後生"},{"pid":"76d58dc116692fda4cdb76b55e6fb97c01298c33","tid":1615543,"uid":32220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32c2355c6779150535106219b317657977db173a","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"34049f8ecbeadc1e30b4e70e5f213272664f081f","tid":1615543,"uid":78470,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"琴晚黃大仙個阿伯拎刀斬人都當把刀係垃圾踢走啦<br />\n根本而家淨係砌後生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"之後都冇理? CLS"},{"pid":"45e6a57ba4ba5754f9273da5d5cd8358de46c0dc","tid":1615543,"uid":54528,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:42:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">取消可信證人角色<br />\n取消搜證權力</span></ins></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"cbd1c0c0673ab2334904a6d38860b4616505cab8","tid":1615543,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:42:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4218bf8a30f9113ae7e67f969e0631039eaf708","tid":1615543,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775b94c44c344f78e6faaba1e1f3bd31396638a5","tid":1615543,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"38ba13936f4b8908a405b7ae1010ffa7b208a64a","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:44:29.000Z","msg":"依然得蘋果報 代表咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23005db7be02fbf07669c23b744505ace29676bc","tid":1615543,"uid":111493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:45:32.000Z","msg":"4點答法: 片段未能反映地下白色管係示威者原先持有，惟現場同事係電光火石間已進行急救。警方會有責任對在場白色管進行化驗是否有鐵成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d0805cc15c5b438b99947d7601f6415eb6f355","tid":1615543,"uid":156791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:45:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b3df1c4fcd9d054a4f6cd9ad9533ceea040fcda","tid":1615543,"uid":78470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"32c2355c6779150535106219b317657977db173a","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"34049f8ecbeadc1e30b4e70e5f213272664f081f","tid":1615543,"uid":78470,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"琴晚黃大仙個阿伯拎刀斬人都當把刀係垃圾踢走啦<br />\n根本而家淨係砌後生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:41:46.000Z","msg":"之後都冇理? CLS"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"個廢老比人獅左兩次 上左白車 之後唔知點"},{"pid":"f26368a8ac2da9805c79d1c44f070273b25493b0","tid":1615543,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:46:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fbd227e23d5cd9666ce29a2b65c55145deea452","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e30b79a8c04dfb62e9150eb92f850d7f6ce847e","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:48:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">執法部門<br />\n法治</span>"},{"pid":"486604a0cd6fb2913e32776ee9ab8bec5657e93e","tid":1615543,"uid":293227,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:48:15.000Z","msg":"屌如果冇記者影撚住，佢印被捕手足指模上去都得啦on9 。<br />\n<br />\n阻採訪或見律師一定要煲大，好撚嚴重"},{"pid":"3beb2fc8dd317f1abf8a5535dde46b68dfe08c12","tid":1615543,"uid":161430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191003/large/1570069602_63a9.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191003/large/1570069602_e0c9.jpg\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推呀 有曬清晰既圖</span>"},{"pid":"debba20da61f54973cd3c00729b5d8b22e29e517","tid":1615543,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:51:09.000Z","msg":"推上報"},{"pid":"04260567437b3b6682579a395b871f0eea16680e","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:52:06.000Z","msg":"中五學生曾志健（健仔）前日（1日）在荃灣遭防暴警近距離開實彈，射穿肺部，情況一度危殆。警察公共關係科總警司謝振中昨（2日）在記者會上辯稱，警員是在生命受威脅情況下開槍，又指施襲者當時以各種武器，包括削尖的行山杖插向警員。不過，法新社記者拍攝到相信為中槍者於衝突前的相片，當時他持手疑似浮版的盾牌，右手則只持一支白色幼身棍狀物，外形似是一般家具組件，並非謝振中所指的「削尖」武器。<br />\n<br />\n此外，警務處副處長（行動）鄧炳強昨又聲稱，警員被襲擊期間有被「搶槍」危險。不過綜合當日港大學生會校園電視，《紐約時報》、城大編委、城大城市廣播拍攝到的事發前後經過，可見一名持長盾防暴警在大河道祥興記生煎包店外被黑衣人追趕時跌倒，其後多名黑衣人上前，一隊防暴警員隨即前來增援，並施放催淚彈驅趕黑衣人。一名黑衣人期間向一名舉槍警揮動白色幼身棍狀物，揮中警員衣袖，警員即開槍。中槍黑衣人向後跌在之前跌倒的的警員身上，其他黑衣人則散開。其中一名黑衣人其後走近中槍者時，被一名防暴警撲低。片段未有見到黑衣人有意圖「搶槍」。"},{"pid":"654baea681add034af3962a66a9b88d4d461f991","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3beb2fc8dd317f1abf8a5535dde46b68dfe08c12","tid":1615543,"uid":161430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191003/large/1570069602_63a9.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191003/large/1570069602_e0c9.jpg\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推呀 有曬清晰既圖</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:53:07.000Z","msg":"記者會變削尖的鐵枝"},{"pid":"c7aee826ed49c4501e3922108767c9533bfa3fdf","tid":1615543,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:55:17.000Z","msg":"pusg."},{"pid":"c858aac3c81c99a2e75fd37c28bd7835e34765ee","tid":1615543,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"654baea681add034af3962a66a9b88d4d461f991","tid":1615543,"uid":15696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3beb2fc8dd317f1abf8a5535dde46b68dfe08c12","tid":1615543,"uid":161430,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191003/large/1570069602_63a9.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191003/large/1570069602_e0c9.jpg\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推呀 有曬清晰既圖</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:53:07.000Z","msg":"記者會變削尖的鐵枝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6d0559d54829e44f9a8fc70026dc7d5dffcc439d","tid":1615543,"uid":35233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c9c4cd67474f41d6462bf0f49b35713b4c2ea0","tid":1615543,"uid":281417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T06:57:01.000Z",